summary:
I am a 22 year old Bolivian born Spanish art student in Rotterdam, passionate about Art and Business. 
Educated through the European School system from 2008 in Luxembourg to 2017 in Culham, UK with a Baccalaureate specialising in Art, Geography, English, Spanish, French, and Math. 
I have undertaken the Foundation one year programme at the Abingdon and Witney College of Arts in the UK from 2018 to 2019 and finished with a Distinction.
I am currently in the second year of my Fine Art degree at the WdKA Rotterdam as well as working freelance through my art studio platforms.
